cope Architecture","categoryPathComponent":"StatoscopeTutorial","role":"project","title":"Single entry point and\/or middlewares"},"kind":"project","sections":[{"kind":"hero","title":"Single entry point and\/or middlewares","chapter":"Tutorials","estimatedTimeInMinutes":30,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Understand how the single entry point enables pretty interesting features"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"tasks","tasks":[{"stepsSection":[{"type":"step","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Let’s grab our first counter example adding some error throwing to illustrate the current example.","type":"text"}]}],"code":"01-03-01-code-0001.swift","runtimePreview":null,"caption":[],"media":null},{"caption":[],"type":"step","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"And the CounterView with no protection to avoid the throw."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"media":null,"code":"01-03-01-code-0002.swift","runtimePreview":null},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A middleware can be added to trap all events in the scope. Logging is straightforward,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"either for terminal logging, analytics, or crash reports."}]}],"media":null,"type":"step","runtimePreview":null,"caption":[],"code":"01-03-01-code-0003.swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Having a comprehensive crash and analytics reporting is mandatory in production apps.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"A single entry point\/middleware enables easy implementation for these features.","type":"text"}]}],"contentSection":[{"kind":"contentAndMedia","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Logging is an important part of the code. Debugging is great, but sometimes the scheduler"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is affected by our breakpoints, and having understandable logs may help us getting rid of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"some bugs."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"mediaPosition":"trailing"}],"title":"Logging middleware","anchor":"Logging-middleware"},{"contentSection":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The error reporting added in the previous step is great. Terminal logging however is unnecessary."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Statoscope has a built in feature for logging. See how to use it."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"contentAndMedia","mediaPosition":"trailing"}],"title":"Built-in Library logging","stepsSection":[{"code":"01-03-01-code-0004.swift","runtimePreview":null,"type":"step","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable the logging globally inyour app."}]}],"caption":[],"media":null},{"type":"step","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the output of the terminal when playing around with the app."}]}],"caption":[],"media":null,"runtimePreview":null,"code":"01-03-01-code-0005.txt"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The single entry point enables Statoscope to build many of its features internally.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"A middleware can be added to the Statostore so user can also benefit from the single entry point."}]}],"anchor":"Built-in-Library-logging"}]},{"title":"Dependency Injection","featuredEyebrow":"Tutorial","kind":"callToAction","abstract":[{"text":"Learn how to easily design dependencies and inject them into your scopes. Dependency injection simplifies the structure of your code by externalizing the management of dependencies, making your code more modular, testable, and flexible. In this tutorial, we will demonstrate dependency injection using an example of a simple news feed application.","type":"text"}],"action":{"overridingTitle":"Get started","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"Get started","type":"text"}],"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Statoscope\/tutorial